<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" ?><document><annotations itct="CAAQwOYBIhMInu7Qmb603wIVTJrBCh07yA6gKPgdMgJpdkiCwpDUnrXevTk">
<annotation id="annotation_165299" type="text" style="popup" log_data="xble=1&amp;ei=oLoeXJ6eIcy0hga7kLuACg&amp;a-v=OXt5qeqEIQI&amp;a-type=1&amp;a-id=annotation_165299" itct="CAEQs-UBGP___________wEiEwie7tCZvrTfAhVMmsEKHTvIDqAo-B0yAml2SILCkNSetd69OQ">
  <TEXT>Here&#39;s yet another gimmick that&#39;s never seen again for the rest of the game. These arrow-sections pull you upwards with a rather surprising amount of speed. This can actually be a problem for a few reasons...</TEXT>
  <segment>
    <movingRegion type="rect">
      <rectRegion x="0.00000" y="0.00000" w="100.00000" h="22.22200" t="0:09:33.3"/>
      <rectRegion x="0.00000" y="0.00000" w="100.00000" h="22.22200" t="0:09:38.3"/>
    </movingRegion>
  </segment>
  <appearance bgAlpha="0.600000023842" bgColor="0" fgColor="16777215" textSize="3.9116" effects="textdropshadow">
    <padding top="2.34696006775" left="2.05074167252" bottom="2.34696006775" right="2.73432230949"/>
  </appearance>
  
</annotation>
<annotation id="annotation_293878" type="text" style="popup" log_data="xble=1&amp;ei=oLoeXJ6eIcy0hga7kLuACg&amp;a-v=OXt5qeqEIQI&amp;a-type=1&amp;a-id=annotation_293878" itct="CAIQs-UBGP___________wEiEwie7tCZvrTfAhVMmsEKHTvIDqAo-B0yAml2SILCkNSetd69OQ">
  <TEXT>First, there are sections where you need to cross gaps between these arrows, as you&#39;ll see here. It&#39;s actually possible to gain too much/too little of inertia from these things that you can literally fall off the screen when you try to make it to the next section. As such...well, I think you know what I&#39;ll be using to get around these...</TEXT>
  <segment>
    <movingRegion type="rect">
      <rectRegion x="0.00000" y="0.00000" w="100.00000" h="31.11100" t="0:09:39.8"/>
      <rectRegion x="0.00000" y="0.00000" w="100.00000" h="31.11100" t="0:09:52.8"/>
    </movingRegion>
  </segment>
  <appearance bgAlpha="0.600000023842" bgColor="0" fgColor="16777215" textSize="3.9116" effects="textdropshadow">
    <padding top="2.34696006775" left="2.05074167252" bottom="2.34696006775" right="2.73432230949"/>
  </appearance>
  
</annotation>
<annotation id="annotation_305142" type="text" style="popup" log_data="xble=1&amp;ei=oLoeXJ6eIcy0hga7kLuACg&amp;a-v=OXt5qeqEIQI&amp;a-type=1&amp;a-id=annotation_305142" itct="CAMQs-UBGP___________wEiEwie7tCZvrTfAhVMmsEKHTvIDqAo-B0yAml2SILCkNSetd69OQ">
  <TEXT>Yes, I had to stop myself from jumping down there at the last moment. The pit actually contains a spike-drop section - and a rather obnoxious one at that.</TEXT>
  <segment>
    <movingRegion type="rect">
      <rectRegion x="0.00000" y="0.00000" w="100.00000" h="17.77800" t="0:07:06.0"/>
      <rectRegion x="0.00000" y="0.00000" w="100.00000" h="17.77800" t="0:07:12.0"/>
    </movingRegion>
  </segment>
  <appearance bgAlpha="0.600000023842" bgColor="0" fgColor="16777215" textSize="3.9116" effects="textdropshadow">
    <padding top="2.34696006775" left="2.05074167252" bottom="2.34696006775" right="2.73432230949"/>
  </appearance>
  
</annotation>
<annotation id="annotation_387029" type="text" style="popup" log_data="xble=1&amp;ei=oLoeXJ6eIcy0hga7kLuACg&amp;a-v=OXt5qeqEIQI&amp;a-type=1&amp;a-id=annotation_387029" itct="CAQQs-UBGP___________wEiEwie7tCZvrTfAhVMmsEKHTvIDqAo-B0yAml2SILCkNSetd69OQ">
  <TEXT>Before I head into the next section, I want you to keep something in mind: In this game, Sniper Joe has the ability to follow you relentlessly via jumping, meaning he can be difficult to get around at times. Why do I bring this up now? Well...</TEXT>
  <segment>
    <movingRegion type="rect">
      <rectRegion x="0.00000" y="0.00000" w="100.00000" h="22.22200" t="0:03:51.9"/>
      <rectRegion x="0.00000" y="0.00000" w="100.00000" h="22.22200" t="0:03:59.9"/>
    </movingRegion>
  </segment>
  <appearance bgAlpha="0.600000023842" bgColor="0" fgColor="16777215" textSize="3.9116" effects="textdropshadow">
    <padding top="2.34696006775" left="2.05074167252" bottom="2.34696006775" right="2.73432230949"/>
  </appearance>
  
</annotation>
<annotation id="annotation_428193" type="text" style="popup" log_data="xble=1&amp;ei=oLoeXJ6eIcy0hga7kLuACg&amp;a-v=OXt5qeqEIQI&amp;a-type=1&amp;a-id=annotation_428193" itct="CAUQs-UBGP___________wEiEwie7tCZvrTfAhVMmsEKHTvIDqAo-B0yAml2SILCkNSetd69OQ">
  <TEXT>Also, it&#39;s worth noting that you actually get sent back to the shop each time you complete a fortress stage. This is also the reason why I have full weapon energy after this. For the sake of convenience, I&#39;ll be editing out the forced shop visits unless I buy something.</TEXT>
  <segment>
    <movingRegion type="rect">
      <rectRegion x="0.00000" y="0.00000" w="100.00000" h="26.94400" t="0:06:06.6"/>
      <rectRegion x="0.00000" y="0.00000" w="100.00000" h="26.94400" t="0:06:14.6"/>
    </movingRegion>
  </segment>
  <appearance bgAlpha="0.600000023842" bgColor="0" fgColor="16777215" textSize="3.9116" effects="textdropshadow">
    <padding top="2.34696006775" left="2.05074167252" bottom="2.34696006775" right="2.73432230949"/>
  </appearance>
  
</annotation>
